{"title":"New Castelli Premio Black bibshorts aim for ultimate (minimalist) comfort on long rides","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/25/new-castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-aim-for-ultimate-minimalist-comfort-on-long-rides/","date":1621929656000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>By paring down the bibshort to just a few pieces of fabric, the new Castelli Premio Black bike shorts provide maximum comfort with minimal material.</p><p>The main body of the shorts is just three pieces of fabric…one for each leg, plus a front panel. And the fabric itself is lighter and thinner thanks to an exclusive new “engineered” weaving process that allows them to change the nature of the material throughout each panel.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels.jpg\" alt=\"individual fabric panels and parts for new 2021 castelli premio black cycling shorts\" width=\"870\" height=\"1015\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels.jpg 870w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-257x300.jpg 257w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-800x933.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-103x120.jpg 103w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-768x896.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-696x812.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-360x420.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels.jpg 870w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-257x300.jpg 257w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-800x933.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-103x120.jpg 103w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-768x896.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-696x812.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131453/castelli-premio-black-bibshorts-fabric-panels-360x420.jpg 360w\"></a></p><p>Meaning, the Lycra is woven closer to the inside face at the leg openings, adding grip without having to apply a silicone gripper afterward. Above that, it gets thinner and lighter, with bands added for both aerodynamics and compression around your quads.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of fabric panels and parts for new 2021 castelli premio black cycling shorts\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-1068x1068.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-420x420.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-1068x1068.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131458/castelli-premio-black-fabric-gripper-panel-420x420.jpg 420w\"></a></p><p>The seat of the shorts is densier and thicker to offer more overall compression around your hips and to help the pad stay in place. They say that compared to knit fabrics, their woven technology results in a lighter, thinner fabric that helps keep you cooler without sacrificing any performance.</p><figure id=\"attachment_259790\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-259790\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-se