mgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-297x149.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-800x401.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-120x60.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-768x384.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-1536x769.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-696x348.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-1068x535.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131535/castelli-progetto-x2-air-seamless-chamois-pad-2021-839x420.jpg 839w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-259790\">Men’s version on the left, women’s on the right.</figcaption></figure><p>Two other details set the shorts apart. First is the latest version of their Progetto X2 Air chamois, which uses a two-layer design to keep a softer fabric against the skin. Under that is a mix of soft- and medium-density foams plus three small gel pads at key pressure points.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of fabric panels and parts for new 2021 castelli premio black cycling shorts\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131504/castelli-premio-black-fabric-strap-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The second are these bonded-and-stitched strap reinforcements. At first glance, they seem superfluous for a short that’s trying to eliminate anything extra. But, they serve to keep the straps laying flat against your skin, so they won’t bunch up over the course of the ride.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p>As for logos on the outside, they’re laser etched so that they won’t fade over time.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-b