o-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-297x145.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-800x391.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-768x375.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-1536x751.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-696x340.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-1068x522.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-859x420.jpg 859w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131509/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-bibshorts-1-533x261.jpg 533w\"></a></p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>The waist sits high, and it’s also seamless, leading into a mesh upper back panel. It’s perforated, not a knit, and then it’s bonded to the lowers without any stitching. On the front, it’s a seamlessly cut edge with some sections folded over for additional comfort.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts.jpg\" alt=\"2021 castelli premio black cycling bibshorts for women\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1090\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-297x202.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-800x545.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-120x82.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-768x523.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-1536x1046.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-218x150.jpg 218w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24131528/castelli-premio-black-ultralight-womens-cycling-bibs-and-shorts-696x474.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.a